<br>
To make things a bit more fair here make something like CotH and see what mages would say as well. Obviously this will be another spell thats going to be extremely difficult to do and have a level associated with it to be much lower than the risk involved. All the places listed above will require 2-3 groups minimum to even reach. How many people have been all the way down to Yael for instance? Not many. Its very difficult to get into the old Paineel city without some real thought and practice just to make it that far. No, I am afraid theres a difference between a quest and a small spell epic - which this definitely compares to. A small epic based quest for a spell. What other class has been punished so?<br>
