<br>
We are tired of flipping a coin to see if a mob can channel through 30+ people pushing it and gate.  Without the pushing strategy, the only other option is let one person tank while the chanters seive it, else you do dmg too quickly and the chanters can't seive fast enough.  These spells are most certainly worth it to raids.  Now for the xp group, like others have said, I don't see as much of a need.  But once you get to mobs that can't be stunned, its a whole different game. <p>Lern Cyberton <br>
